'''Pitni''' ar '''pikni''' ar ''' pikini''' (frah [[Puotigiis]] ''pequenino'', sumaal wan), sohtaim refa tu az '''chail''', bailajikali a yuuman biin bitwiin di stiej a [[boert]] ah [[piubati]]. Di liigal definishan a ''pitni'' jinarali refa tu a [[Maina (laa)|maina]], adawaiz nuo az smadi yongga dah di [[iej a majariti]].

''Pitni'' kiah diskraib azwel rilieshanship wid a pierant (laka [[son]] ah [[daata]] a ''h''eni iej)<ref>[http://www.ssa.gov/dibplan/dacpage.shtml For example, the US Social Security department  specifically defines an adult child as being over 18] Ssa.gov axes 2013-10-09</ref> ar, metafarikali, wah aatariti figa, ar signifai gruup membaship ina klan, chraib, ar rilijan; ikiah signifai azwel smadi uu afek ar influens chrang-chrang bai spisifik taim, plies, ar soerkomstans, laka "niecha pitni" ar "Sixtiz pitni".

A nof suoshal ishu afek pitni, laka [[Hoerli chailud edikieshan|chailud edikieshan]], buliyin, pavati, disfongshanal [[faambli]], [[chail lieba]], ah [[ongga]]. Pitni kiah riez bai [[pierans]], fasta pierans, [[Liigal gyaadian|gyaadian]] ar riez paashali ina [[die kier]] senta.

